title: Bobby Gets Text from Ronnie Dunn That’s Been Weighing on Him + Arkansas Keith Talks About Bobby Eating Squirrel As A Kid + Eddie Has A Serious Problem with His Foster Kid
itunes:title: Bobby Gets Text from Ronnie Dunn That’s Been Weighing on Him + Arkansas Keith Talks About Bobby Eating Squirrel As A Kid + Eddie Has A Serious Problem with His Foster Kid
description:
Ronnie Dunn texted Bobby and said he gets to choose 2 songs for Brooks and Dunn to play at the Raging Idiots Million Dollar Show…and it’s weighing on him. Bobby’s stepdad Arkansas Keith calls to talk about the way Bobby grew up. Eddie brings in a serious problem he his having with his foster kid…who wants a Tom Brady Jersey for Christmas.
